&lt;p&gt;You are living comfortably at your home.  &lt;br&gt;
You have inquisitiveness to know the world around  &lt;br&gt;
So you go out and travel as far places as you want to know.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While on the journey you feel you have to eat to survive  &lt;br&gt;
But you need money to eat and pay for  &lt;br&gt;
your temporary stay at different hotels.  &lt;br&gt;
For that, you need to earn money.  &lt;br&gt;
You learn some useful arts and skills.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
